 Aegis 1.0.0 "Ambient Argus"

 This is v1 software -- a first public release, not
 production-hardened. The C kernel likely contains real,
 exploitable vulnerabilities. Do not deploy on untrusted
 networks or with real secrets.

 A gradual Rust migration is underway. Contributions welcome
 at https://github.com/exec/aegis

